cross validation on train data

1.finetune original models on pseudo labeled test set. > output/MODEL_DIR/finetuned_model
2.train finetuned model on all train data. > output/MODEL_DIR/final_model
3.cross validate final_model on train data. > output/MODEL_DIR/final_model/cross_validation_results
4.test final model on test data. > output/MODEL_DIR/final_model


random 9-1 validation on train data

1.train and eval original model on random split train data. > random_split_output/MODEL_DIR/model
2.cross validate final_model on train data. > random_split_output/MODEL_DIR/model/cross_validation_results
3.test final model on test data. > random_split_output/MODEL_DIR/model